{
  "id": "5cfb42379b980900178aabbb",
  "title": "労働時間効率",
  "created": 1559970376,
  "updated": 1560224856,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cfb42379b980900178aabbb",
      "text": "労働時間効率",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970376,
      "updated": 1559972161
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4248aff09e0000689ee0",
      "text": ">「働き方」と「豊かさ」の関係。有名な思考実験ですが、一週間働く漁師の漁獲高は、A＝毎日８時間、B＝毎日目標数だけ、C＝穫れる日に沢山働いて後は休むで、Ｃ＞Ａ＞Ｂの順になる。「ノルマ決めてガンバる」のが最悪、「定時間働く」が次善。企業組織の働き方はそもそも生産性が低いという。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970376,
      "updated": 1559970402
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb425aaff09e0000689ee2",
      "text": "\thttps://twitter.com/shu_yamaguchi/status/1136756720980520960",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970395,
      "updated": 1559970395
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4258aff09e0000689ee1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970392,
      "updated": 1559970392
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4263aff09e0000689ee3",
      "text": "一定時間あたりの収穫量が1〜7だとする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970403,
      "updated": 1559970424
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4271aff09e0000689ee5",
      "text": "\t(A) 毎日25単位時間働く場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970417,
      "updated": 1559970705
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb429baff09e0000689ee6",
      "text": "\t\t収穫の合計は700",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970459,
      "updated": 1559970555
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb42fbaff09e0000689ee7",
      "text": "\t\t労働時間の合計は175",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970556,
      "updated": 1559970574
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb430daff09e0000689ee8",
      "text": "\t\t単位時間あたりの収穫効率は4.0",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970574,
      "updated": 1559970583
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4317aff09e0000689ee9",
      "text": "\t(B) 毎日100収穫をノルマとして働く場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970584,
      "updated": 1559970707
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4322aff09e0000689eea",
      "text": "\t\tそれぞれの日の労働時間(単位未満は切り上げ)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970595,
      "updated": 1559970662
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb426daff09e0000689ee4",
      "text": "\t\t\t`array([100.,  50.,  34.,  25.,  20.,  17.,  15.])`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970413,
      "updated": 1559970654
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4356aff09e0000689eeb",
      "text": "\t\t合計労働時間は261",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970646,
      "updated": 1559970698
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4385aff09e0000689eec",
      "text": "\t\t収穫の合計は700",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970694,
      "updated": 1559970717
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb439daff09e0000689eee",
      "text": "\t\t\t(A)と変わらない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970718,
      "updated": 1559970721
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb43a1aff09e0000689eef",
      "text": "\t\t単位時間あたりの収穫効率は2.68",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970721,
      "updated": 1559970738
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb46a4aff09e0000689f0b",
      "text": "\t\t\t(A) > (B)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971492,
      "updated": 1559971496
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb43b4aff09e0000689ef0",
      "text": "\t(C) 獲れるときにたくさん働く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970740,
      "updated": 1559970767
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb43cfaff09e0000689ef1",
      "text": "\t\t(B)で、最大100単位時間働いているので同じ時間を最良の効率の日に働いたとする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970767,
      "updated": 1559970903
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4467aff09e0000689ef3",
      "text": "\t\tそれぞれの日の労働時間(単位未満は切り上げ)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970919,
      "updated": 1559970919
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4467aff09e0000689ef4",
      "text": "\t\t\t`array([0.,  0.,  0.,  0.,  0.,  0.,  100.])`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970919,
      "updated": 1559970935
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4480aff09e0000689ef7",
      "text": "\t\t合計労働時間は100",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970944,
      "updated": 1559970948
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb447eaff09e0000689ef5",
      "text": "\t\t収穫の合計は700",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970943,
      "updated": 1559970943
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb447eaff09e0000689ef6",
      "text": "\t\t\t(A)(B)と変わらない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970943,
      "updated": 1559970959
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4458aff09e0000689ef2",
      "text": "\t\t単位時間あたりの収穫効率は7.0",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970905,
      "updated": 1559970964
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb46abaff09e0000689f0c",
      "text": "\t\t (C) > (A) > (B)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971500,
      "updated": 1559971504
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb439caff09e0000689eed",
      "text": "\t(C2) 獲れるときにたくさん働く、その2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970716,
      "updated": 1559971220
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb44a2aff09e0000689ef9",
      "text": "\t\t「とはいえ、最良の効率のときだけ働くなんてできないじゃん」という意見を想定",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559970978,
      "updated": 1559971229
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb44ddaff09e0000689efa",
      "text": "\t\t毎日20単位時間働いて、調子がよかったら30時間まで延長する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971037,
      "updated": 1559971087
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4511aff09e0000689efb",
      "text": "\t\t\t「25単位働く」が10時間労働のイメージ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971089,
      "updated": 1559971176
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4550aff09e0000689efc",
      "text": "\t\t\t「20単位働いて調子が良ければ30単位」は「8時間働いて、調子が良ければ4時間残業」のイメージ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971152,
      "updated": 1559971190
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb45c0aff09e0000689eff",
      "text": "\t\t\t「調子が良い」は「単位時間あたりの収穫が4より大きい」とする。20単位働いている間に確認できる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971264,
      "updated": 1559971293
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb45e3aff09e0000689f01",
      "text": "\t\t20単位時間の収穫",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971300,
      "updated": 1559971362
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4621aff09e0000689f03",
      "text": "\t\t\t`array([ 20,  40,  60,  80, 100, 120, 140])`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971362,
      "updated": 1559971364
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4649aff09e0000689f07",
      "text": "\t\t\t合計560",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971402,
      "updated": 1559971404
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4624aff09e0000689f04",
      "text": "\t\t残業時間の収穫",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971364,
      "updated": 1559971368
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4628aff09e0000689f05",
      "text": "\t\t\t`array([ 0,  0,  0,  0, 50, 60, 70])`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971368,
      "updated": 1559971375
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb464daff09e0000689f08",
      "text": "\t\t\t合計180",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971405,
      "updated": 1559971409
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4630aff09e0000689f06",
      "text": "\t\t収穫合計740",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971376,
      "updated": 1559971424
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4662aff09e0000689f09",
      "text": "\t\t合計労働時間は170",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971426,
      "updated": 1559971439
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4684aff09e0000689f0a",
      "text": "\t\t収穫効率は4.35",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971460,
      "updated": 1559971468
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4621aff09e0000689f02",
      "text": "\t\t\t(C) > (C2) > (A) > (B)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971362,
      "updated": 1559971522
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb46b4aff09e0000689f0d",
      "text": "\t(C3) 獲れるときにたくさん働く、その3",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971508,
      "updated": 1559971869
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb46feaff09e0000689f0e",
      "text": "\t\tもっと労働時間の変動を大きくしてみる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971582,
      "updated": 1559971633
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb470eaff09e0000689f10",
      "text": "\t\t\t「午前に2時間働いてみて調子が悪ければ半休を取る」イメージ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971599,
      "updated": 1559971617
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4729aff09e0000689f12",
      "text": "\t\t\t毎日5単位時間働いて、調子がよかったら25時間働らく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971625,
      "updated": 1559971672
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4759aff09e0000689f16",
      "text": "\t\t5単位時間の収穫",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971673,
      "updated": 1559971761
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47b0aff09e0000689f17",
      "text": "\t\t\t`array([ 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35])`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971761,
      "updated": 1559971762
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47b2aff09e0000689f18",
      "text": "\t\t\t合計140",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971763,
      "updated": 1559971769
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47b9aff09e0000689f19",
      "text": "\t\t調子の良い日の追加20時間の収穫",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971769,
      "updated": 1559971781
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47c5aff09e0000689f1a",
      "text": "\t\t\t`array([  0,   0,   0,   0, 100, 120, 140])`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971781,
      "updated": 1559971802
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47daaff09e0000689f1b",
      "text": "\t\t\t合計360",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971803,
      "updated": 1559971809
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47e0aff09e0000689f1c",
      "text": "\t\t収穫合計 500",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971809,
      "updated": 1559971815
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb47e8aff09e0000689f1d",
      "text": "\t\t労働時間合計 95",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971817,
      "updated": 1559971841
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4801aff09e0000689f1e",
      "text": "\t\t収穫効率 5.26",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971842,
      "updated": 1559971861
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4815aff09e0000689f1f",
      "text": "\t\t\t(C) > (C3) > (C2) > (A) > (B)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971862,
      "updated": 1559971881
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4729aff09e0000689f13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971625,
      "updated": 1559971666
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb482aaff09e0000689f20",
      "text": "まとめ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971882,
      "updated": 1559971884
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb482baff09e0000689f22",
      "text": "\t単位時間あたりの収穫量が変動する状況",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971884,
      "updated": 1559971954
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4872aff09e0000689f23",
      "text": "\t働き方をするかによって単位労働時間あたりの収穫量が変わる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971954,
      "updated": 1559971964
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb48feaff09e0000689f2d",
      "text": "\t\t(C) > (C3) > (C2) > (A) > (B)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972094,
      "updated": 1559972095
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb487caff09e0000689f24",
      "text": "\t\t(B)「一定収穫量に達するまで働らく」が最悪",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971964,
      "updated": 1559972084
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb4898aff09e0000689f26",
      "text": "\t\t\t単位時間あたりの収穫量が低いときに集中的に働くことになるから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559971992,
      "updated": 1559972010
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb48abaff09e0000689f27",
      "text": "\t\t(A)「一定時間を働く」が次に悪い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972012,
      "updated": 1559972088
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb48b6aff09e0000689f29",
      "text": "\t\t(C)「単位時間あたりの収穫量が高いときに集中して働く」が最も効率が良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972022,
      "updated": 1559972090
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb48e2aff09e0000689f2a",
      "text": "\t\t\tただし、現実的にそれができるか疑問を持つ人も多かろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972066,
      "updated": 1559972078
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb48efaff09e0000689f2c",
      "text": "\t\t(C2)「調子のいいときに残業をし、調子の悪い日は定時で上がる」は(A)よりまし",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972080,
      "updated": 1559972126
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb491eaff09e0000689f2e",
      "text": "\t\t(C3)「調子の悪いときには午後半休をとり、調子のいいときに残業をする」が(C)の次に良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972126,
      "updated": 1559972153
    },
    {
      "id": "5cff2456aff09e000068621e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1560224855,
      "updated": 1560224856
    },
    {
      "id": "5cfb48eeaff09e0000689f2b",
      "text": "[ドルコスト平均法]の逆パターン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1559972078,
      "updated": 1560224853
    },
    {
      "id": "5cff2444aff09e000068621d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1560224836,
      "updated": 1560224836
    }
  ]
}